limits:
no limit on number of youtube videos uploaded
limit on number of channels: 50 <- use as category
limit on number of playlists:
	1000 <- people
	https://developers.google.com/youtube/v3/docs/playlists no limit
	create playlist as tags and put video under multile playlists, but tags can be thousands
limit on number of videos under a playlists
	3600 videos tried,
	5000 <- people
you can only sync up to 3,333 songs per device on up to three devices.




